692
00:39:10,744 --> 00:39:12,675
You know, holidays.
Jamie never gets home at all.

693
00:39:12,935 --> 00:39:15,210
I think we wives should form a union.
- You're right.

694
00:39:15,527 --> 00:39:17,094
Goodnight, dear.
- Bye-bye.

695
00:39:24,333 --> 00:39:26,178
I wonder what happened
to Bill Briggs tonight.

696
00:39:27,136 --> 00:39:29,386
