He phoned earlier.

697
00:39:29,872 --> 00:39:31,967
He said he wanted to come
but he just wasn't up to it.

698
00:39:32,370 --> 00:39:33,909
I wish you'd called me to the phone.

699
00:39:34,164 --> 00:39:36,324
I wanted to talk to him anyway.
- Darling, you were busy.

700
00:39:36,649 --> 00:39:37,664
I know, but I ..

701
00:39:39,915 --> 00:39:41,962
