702
00:39:42,574 --> 00:39:43,160
No.

703
00:39:43,589 --> 00:39:46,497
He just gravitated towards the
library and made himself cozy.

704
00:39:47,873 --> 00:39:50,110
That sounds a little like
<i>artificial</i> gravitation to me.

705
00:39:50,494 --> 00:39:52,407
