- No, he can't see me like this.

1056
00:58:13,018 --> 00:58:15,812
Fred, help me, help me.
- Alright, I'll take care of him.

1057
00:58:16,363 --> 00:58:18,320
Just lay low for a bit.
I'll see he gets home.

1058
00:58:18,534 --> 00:58:20,042
Say I left early to get some milk.

1059
00:58:20,526 --> 00:58:22,012
Please, Fred. Hurry.
- Be quiet.

1060
00:58:25,612 --> 00:58:28,337
[ Whistling ]

1061
00:58:29,416 --> 00:58:30,488
It's me, Paul.

1062
00:58:31,387 --> 00:58:32,357
Hi, Mr Staples.

1063
00:58:33,549 --> 00:58:35,626
Man, what a place by night.

1064
00:58:36,251 --> 00:58:38,510
Where do they keep the caskets?
- How you doing, partner?

1065
00:58:38,878 --> 00:58:40,609
Dad said I should drop
in and pick him up.

1066
00:58:41,780 --> 00:58:43,482
He went on home.
He needed a little rest.

1067
00:58:45,105 --> 00:58:45,749
Good.

1068
00:58:46,246 --> 00:58:47,748
