1206
01:06:45,701 --> 01:06:46,345
Bill.

1207
01:06:48,184 --> 01:06:48,885
Please.

1208
01:06:51,570 --> 01:06:52,603
Mister Ramsey.

1209
01:06:54,808 --> 01:06:57,349
I had no intention of
seeming insubordinate.

1210
01:07:14,229 --> 01:07:15,364
